<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> Chyan Yang and Jen-Bor Huang. "A decision model for IS outsourcing", International Journal of Information Management 20- 3 (2000): 225- 239.</li>
<li id="cite_note-16"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16" title="">^</a></b> L. Willcocks, M. Lacity and G. Fitzgerald. "Information technology outsourcing in Europe and the USA: Assessment issues", International Journal of Information Management 15- 5 (1995): 333- 351.</li>
</ol>
</div>
